# Simulate First

Before any transaction broadcast:

1. Run chain-specific simulation (`eth_call`, `simulateTransaction`, NEAR dry-run).
2. Decode revert reasons structurally — do not broadcast on failure.
3. Log simulation result to audit trail before signing via KMS/HSM.
